                            </p>
                          <p>
                              <em>Lorenzo Lotto Portraits / Lorenzo Lotto Retratos</em>, Museo Nacional del Prado, Madrid, 06/19/2018 - 09/30/2018; National Gallery, London, 11/05/2018 - 02/10/2019
